http://www.thehindu.com/news/national/telangana/Kakatiya-College-to-host-INSPIRE/article14005107.ece

The Department of Science and Technology, Government of India, is organising ‘Innovation in Science Pursuit for Inspired Research’ (INSPIRE) internship programme at the Kakatiya Government College, Hanamkonda, from January 20 to 24 to for intermediate students who have secured 92 per cent and above marks in SSC.‘Attract talent’The objective of INSPIRE is to communicate to young population of the country the excitements of creative pursuit of science, and attract the talented students to study science.